## Next Steps

To see Speed Insights data in action:
1. Deploy this application to Vercel
2. Enable Speed Insights in your Vercel project dashboard (Project Settings → Speed Insights → Enable)
3. After deployment and user visits, view performance metrics in the Vercel dashboard

